{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/posts/lets-meet-bot/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code Me, dsewnr","author":"dsewnr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"96d32d77-594b-57e8-814b-f70c54994d85","excerpt":"前情提要 有一天在某個宅宅群組，因為有不少宅宅 relocate 到大台北地區，有宅提議說要辦個宅宅聚餐，但是呢，因為宅宅散佈在大台北各個角落，所以產生了一個問題「A 約的地點 B 說太遠，B 提議的地點 C 說不方便」，哇！這樣不知道要何年何月何日才約的成聚餐 QQ…","html":"<h2>前情提要</h2>\n<p>有一天在某個宅宅群組，因為有不少宅宅 relocate 到大台北地區，有宅提議說要辦個宅宅聚餐，但是呢，因為宅宅散佈在大台北各個角落，所以產生了一個問題「A 約的地點 B 說太遠，B 提議的地點 C 說不方便」，哇！這樣不知道要何年何月何日才約的成聚餐 QQ</p>\n<h2>求解</h2>\n<p>當時腦中就產生一個想法，不如就用算的吧！讓數據來說話最公平！於是就請大家把自己所在的座標傳到群組裡，然後趁著午休吃飯的時間 google 了一番尋找計算的方法，然後就找到這篇「<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/37885798/how-to-calculate-the-midpoint-of-several-geolocations-in-python\">How to calculate the midpoint of several geolocations in python</a>」，計算的方法很簡單，很輕鬆的就找出中心座標！大家也接受了在這座標附近聚餐。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 98.88888888888889%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lets meet gist\"\n        title=\"lets meet gist\"\n        src=\"/static/9ad59e197da2ac1bd2367674ff302d36/80e3c/lets-meet-gist.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9ad59e197da2ac1bd2367674ff302d36/4ec73/lets-meet-gist.jpg 180w,\n/static/9ad59e197da2ac1bd2367674ff302d36/158ba/lets-meet-gist.jpg 360w,\n/static/9ad59e197da2ac1bd2367674ff302d36/80e3c/lets-meet-gist.jpg 720w,\n/static/9ad59e197da2ac1bd2367674ff302d36/47311/lets-meet-gist.jpg 1080w,\n/static/9ad59e197da2ac1bd2367674ff302d36/ec605/lets-meet-gist.jpg 1125w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>當下就在想是不是能做成服務，然後就有人提議 chatbot，這又是另一段故事了(煙)，其實就在下面…</p>\n<h2>Give it a try</h2>\n<p>當天晚上在家有點時間就嘗試弄了隻 prototype，下列是有用到的相關資源：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://core.telegram.org/bots/api\">Telegram Bot API</a> (就官方文件)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/python-telegram-bot/python-telegram-bot\">python-telegram-bot</a> (簡單好用的套件)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://serveo.net/\">serveo</a> (讓我可以在本機接 webhook，另外也可以參考 <a href=\"https://ngrok.com/\">ngrok</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 158.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lets meet prototype\"\n        title=\"lets meet prototype\"\n        src=\"/static/c0e3b5f73a768dd9a4e95225340dfdc8/37523/lets-meet-prototype.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c0e3b5f73a768dd9a4e95225340dfdc8/e9ff0/lets-meet-prototype.png 180w,\n/static/c0e3b5f73a768dd9a4e95225340dfdc8/f21e7/lets-meet-prototype.png 360w,\n/static/c0e3b5f73a768dd9a4e95225340dfdc8/37523/lets-meet-prototype.png 720w,\n/static/c0e3b5f73a768dd9a4e95225340dfdc8/302a4/lets-meet-prototype.png 1080w,\n/static/c0e3b5f73a768dd9a4e95225340dfdc8/78797/lets-meet-prototype.png 1125w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>隔夜 bot</h2>\n<p>隔天晚上也有點時間，就讓 prototype 成型吧！把昨天的 code 改來改去調整了一下，找了張 free icon，寫上想了好一陣子的 bot 介紹，新增了 Dockerfile，然後把它佈到雲上，最後再施了一個 domain 給它，它就上．線．了！至於為什麼 username 是 <a href=\"https://t.me/MeThereBot\">@MeThereBot</a> 呢？因為想到的都被用光了…</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://t.me/MeThereBot\">Let’s Meet Bot</a></h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 89.44444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lets meet bot welcome\"\n        title=\"lets meet bot welcome\"\n        src=\"/static/275565ffc25a2dac4eee3a642714a0ca/37523/lets-meet-bot-welcome.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/275565ffc25a2dac4eee3a642714a0ca/e9ff0/lets-meet-bot-welcome.png 180w,\n/static/275565ffc25a2dac4eee3a642714a0ca/f21e7/lets-meet-bot-welcome.png 360w,\n/static/275565ffc25a2dac4eee3a642714a0ca/37523/lets-meet-bot-welcome.png 720w,\n/static/275565ffc25a2dac4eee3a642714a0ca/84a90/lets-meet-bot-welcome.png 982w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 216.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lets meet bot telegram\"\n        title=\"lets meet bot telegram\"\n        src=\"/static/8b466a705604edc96811824385067695/37523/lets-meet-bot-telegram.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8b466a705604edc96811824385067695/e9ff0/lets-meet-bot-telegram.png 180w,\n/static/8b466a705604edc96811824385067695/f21e7/lets-meet-bot-telegram.png 360w,\n/static/8b466a705604edc96811824385067695/37523/lets-meet-bot-telegram.png 720w,\n/static/8b466a705604edc96811824385067695/302a4/lets-meet-bot-telegram.png 1080w,\n/static/8b466a705604edc96811824385067695/78797/lets-meet-bot-telegram.png 1125w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Q&#x26;A</h2>\n<p>Q: 如果有人故意定位在巴士海峽呢？<br>\nA：誰傳這定位在群組各位他X的還不O爆他</p>\n<p>Q：如果中心點在河裡或海裡要怎麼辦？<br>\nA: 可以找中心附近或離中心最近交通方便的地點r</p>\n<h2>後記</h2>\n<p>這隻 chatbot 有個已知的問題是非常大量的人使用會爆炸！不過等有那一天到的時候再來煩惱吧… BTW, 最近在看<a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/title/80991903\">異獸魔都</a>，真的好讚！<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8OLtM7-VbO8\">Welcome トゥ 混沌</a>！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/BK0tDxrzUOc/maxresdefault.jpg\"></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"幫忙找出中心座標的 Telegram bot","date":"June 06, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lets-meet-bot/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/pass-probation-2020/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"通過三個月試用期"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/awesome-tool-boop/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"發現超好用小工具 Boop！如果沒有它，在 CLI 要如何解決？"}}}}}